The Perfect Workspace

Documentation and Reports:
	GoogleDocs
	ShareLatex

Project Managment:
	Slack (papers, files, messages)
	Trello (tasks)

Version Control:
	github + github-desktop

Coding:
	Text - Sublime Text. Packages are super important:
		Package Control
		SublimeREPL (interperter inside sublime - Matlab/Python etc.)
		SideBar Enhancments (create files / folders from side-bar)
		Alignment (align code, variable assignment etc.)
		Vintageous (Vim emulation - for these who are used to VIM)
		Matlab Completions
		All Autocomplete (complete words from all files in project)
		SublimeLinter (lint code) + mlint (Matlab)
		1337 (Color Scheme)
		Agila (UI theme)
	IDE - for debugging use MATLAB desktop / Pycharm
	Ipython - for presenting the research, and interactive programming

Browsing
	Chrome + Session Buddy
	Google Scholar
